WEBVTT

01:27.400 --> 01:31.850
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.190 --> 01:34.910
[Episode 20]

01:36.229 --> 01:36.880
Honey,

01:37.229 --> 01:38.490
I'm going out for a bit.

01:38.950 --> 01:42.070
Officer Li called yesterday
and asked me to come over today.

01:42.070 --> 01:44.789
I guess there might be some new progress
in Leilei's case,

01:44.789 --> 01:45.509
or

01:45.920 --> 01:47.280
maybe Ding Zhibo's.

01:47.789 --> 01:49.990
I'll grab some groceries on my way home.

02:18.150 --> 02:18.870
Honey.

02:24.190 --> 02:25.000
I'm back.

02:29.430 --> 02:31.160
Why are you sitting in the dark?

02:35.680 --> 02:39.010
Did you ever work as a private tutor
when you were in college?

02:39.520 --> 02:40.150
Yes, I did.

02:41.000 --> 02:43.000
You know
what my family situation was like.

02:43.000 --> 02:45.000
I had to earn my own living expenses.

02:51.240 --> 02:52.770
Did you ever tutor a student

02:53.870 --> 02:55.600
whose mother was named He Xiao?

02:59.310 --> 03:00.470
Why bring her up?

03:00.910 --> 03:02.170
Who told you about her?

03:04.520 --> 03:06.120
Officer Li met with me today.

03:08.110 --> 03:09.030
I thought it was about Leilei

03:09.030 --> 03:10.470
or Ding Zhibo,

03:11.960 --> 03:13.020
but it was neither.

03:15.000 --> 03:16.090
He told me

03:16.840 --> 03:18.260
that the student said

03:19.320 --> 03:22.160
his mother, He Xiao,
abandoned her family for you

03:22.360 --> 03:23.960
and then committed suicide.

03:26.150 --> 03:28.210
He remembered your name is Luo Liang.

03:28.680 --> 03:29.470
He Xiao,

03:30.910 --> 03:33.310
just like Leilei,
who committed suicide for Xia Yi,

03:33.310 --> 03:34.910
was a victim of gaslighting.

03:36.470 --> 03:37.530
Officer Li said...

03:39.360 --> 03:41.910
the one who put together
the complete PUA Theory

03:41.910 --> 03:43.370
goes by the name "Mister."

03:43.870 --> 03:46.070
He's extremely good at reading people—

03:46.710 --> 03:48.520
an absolute professional.

03:51.960 --> 03:53.000
Why are you

03:53.590 --> 03:54.720
telling me all this?

03:56.000 --> 03:57.060
Because they think

03:58.030 --> 03:58.650
you

03:59.079 --> 04:00.320
are Mister.

04:04.520 --> 04:05.650
Do you believe that?

04:06.280 --> 04:07.740
I don't want to believe it.

04:09.080 --> 04:10.690
But that's what they think.

04:13.310 --> 04:14.400
They said that in 2007,

04:14.400 --> 04:16.190
you were studying
at Tianfu Medical University,

04:16.190 --> 04:18.720
and that's when you worked as a tutor.

04:19.269 --> 04:20.470
I've told you before,

04:21.240 --> 04:22.370
if you want to leave,

04:22.870 --> 04:24.070
you can do so anytime.

04:24.950 --> 04:26.000
You know exactly

04:26.000 --> 04:28.400
where our marriage certificates are kept.

04:32.790 --> 04:33.670
Tell me,

04:34.310 --> 04:35.740
is what they said true?

04:40.480 --> 04:41.040
Alright.

04:42.600 --> 04:44.370
I did know He Xiao,

04:44.930 --> 04:46.820
and I did tutor her son.

04:47.380 --> 04:49.580
She indeed left a deep impression on me.

04:53.930 --> 04:56.050
But it wasn't a pleasant one.

05:04.700 --> 05:05.780
He Xiao

05:06.290 --> 05:07.550
was also from Diannan.

05:08.440 --> 05:09.720
Since we were from the same place,

05:09.720 --> 05:11.240
she was very warm toward me

05:11.240 --> 05:12.630
when we first met.

05:14.240 --> 05:15.970
Her husband was rarely at home,

05:16.390 --> 05:17.390
and her son was disobedient

05:17.390 --> 05:18.790
and did poorly in school.

05:19.600 --> 05:20.360
At that time,

05:21.360 --> 05:23.160
I simply felt she had a hard life.

05:23.920 --> 05:27.580
So occasionally, I'd help out
with heavy chores around the house.

05:27.800 --> 05:29.730
She really liked watching movies.

05:30.040 --> 05:32.020
One time when I went to her house,

05:32.800 --> 05:34.630
she said her son had gone to
a classmate's house,

05:34.630 --> 05:36.560
so the lesson would have to be canceled.

05:36.560 --> 05:37.750
But then she said,

05:38.159 --> 05:39.040
since I was already there,

05:39.040 --> 05:40.970
she'd still pay me for the session,

05:41.480 --> 05:43.540
as long as I stayed the full two hours,

05:43.750 --> 05:45.270
like a normal class.

05:47.680 --> 05:49.250
Of course, I agreed.

05:49.480 --> 05:50.920
I was a poor student back then.

05:50.920 --> 05:52.450
I wanted to earn that money.

05:53.920 --> 05:54.980
Later, she asked me

05:55.950 --> 05:58.210
to watch a newly released movie with her,

05:59.080 --> 06:00.280
called "The Reader."

06:06.040 --> 06:07.240
I've seen that movie.

06:08.830 --> 06:11.160
It's about
a young woman and a teenage boy.

06:11.630 --> 06:12.070
Right.

06:12.830 --> 06:13.680
In that movie,

06:14.040 --> 06:14.900
there's a scene

06:15.120 --> 06:17.600
where the two of them
are sitting in the bathtub reading.

06:17.600 --> 06:19.200
She said, since I was a tutor,

06:19.270 --> 06:20.800
she wanted me to read to her.

06:21.390 --> 06:22.800
She had chosen "The Red and the Black"

06:22.800 --> 06:24.070
and "Anna Karenina."

06:26.190 --> 06:27.040
Both books

06:27.750 --> 06:30.480
deal with secret affairs and infidelity.

06:32.510 --> 06:33.810
So you and she...

06:34.720 --> 06:36.320
How could I possibly do that?

06:36.720 --> 06:38.120
You know what I've been through.

06:38.120 --> 06:39.360
I would never let myself

06:39.360 --> 06:42.290
get into that kind of
compromising situation again.

06:43.510 --> 06:46.190
I left without even collecting
the tutoring fee that time.

06:46.190 --> 06:47.650
I quit on my own after that.

06:50.630 --> 06:51.230
That's it?

06:54.510 --> 06:55.390
That's it.

06:57.310 --> 06:58.680
As for what you said—
that she later had an affair

06:58.680 --> 06:59.630
and abandoned her family—

06:59.630 --> 07:01.430
that doesn't surprise me at all.

07:01.560 --> 07:03.220
She was still young back then.

07:03.610 --> 07:06.140
Living like a grass widow
must've been tough.

07:07.680 --> 07:09.160
But I have no idea who she

07:09.160 --> 07:10.290
had the affair with.

07:10.830 --> 07:12.920
And you just said
she took her own life later.

07:12.920 --> 07:14.180
I'm sorry to hear that,

07:14.720 --> 07:16.450
but I know even less about that.

07:20.040 --> 07:20.600
You said

07:21.920 --> 07:23.310
those cops think I'm...

07:24.360 --> 07:25.000
"Mister"?

07:26.310 --> 07:29.040
Killing people
through romantic manipulation?

07:29.390 --> 07:30.650
I think that's absurd.

07:31.750 --> 07:32.830
Look at you.

07:34.040 --> 07:36.040
Aren't you still alive and well?

07:42.870 --> 07:43.800
Come on.

07:44.870 --> 07:45.680
Let it go.

07:58.390 --> 07:58.920
Alright.

08:03.040 --> 08:04.570
I shouldn't have said this.

08:07.030 --> 08:08.090
That Officer Li...

08:10.000 --> 08:11.210
once came to see me

08:12.720 --> 08:13.510
as a patient.

08:15.630 --> 08:17.070
He has PTSD.

08:19.240 --> 08:20.300
It's highly likely

08:20.360 --> 08:22.240
that he's being sidelined at work.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.390
He's desperate to solve a big case

08:23.390 --> 08:24.720
and transfer out of that precinct.

08:24.720 --> 08:26.270
I don't know the exact reason,

08:26.270 --> 08:27.670
but what I can be sure of is

08:27.870 --> 08:30.330
that he's in a very unstable state
right now.

08:31.070 --> 08:33.330
He sees everyone as a potential suspect.

08:37.150 --> 08:38.270
If you don't believe me,

08:38.270 --> 08:40.080
you can go to the hospital
with me tomorrow.

08:40.080 --> 08:42.390
I'll have the nurse pull up his records
from that day for you,

08:42.390 --> 08:44.550
so he won't be able to deny it
when you confront him.

08:44.550 --> 08:45.210
Afterward,

08:45.480 --> 08:47.870
if he reports me
for breaching his medical privacy

08:47.870 --> 08:48.790
and I lose my job over it,

08:48.790 --> 08:49.790
I won't blame you.

08:50.480 --> 08:51.870
It's just a job.

08:52.080 --> 08:54.540
It's not as important as
earning your trust.

09:02.360 --> 09:04.090
I really despise those people.

09:04.920 --> 09:06.480
If they believe I committed a crime,

09:06.480 --> 09:08.240
they can just present evidence
and arrest me.

09:08.240 --> 09:09.910
But sneaking around behind my back,
whispering to my wife,

09:09.910 --> 09:10.440
trying to drive a wedge between us—

09:10.440 --> 09:12.100
what kind of behavior is that?

09:12.550 --> 09:14.880
If you think you've been wrongly accused,

09:15.630 --> 09:17.960
you can go to Officer Li
to clear your name

09:18.080 --> 09:19.740
and let them investigate you.

09:20.630 --> 09:21.630
Why should I?

09:22.030 --> 09:23.600
And how am I supposed to clear my name?

09:23.600 --> 09:24.840
You just said it yourself—

09:24.840 --> 09:25.840
that's simply what they think!

09:25.840 --> 09:27.040
What can I do about it?

09:27.240 --> 09:28.040
Just like you—

09:28.080 --> 09:29.270
you had no way to clarify the matter

09:29.270 --> 09:30.200
with Ding Zhibo!

09:30.200 --> 09:31.240
You didn't want to explain!

09:31.240 --> 09:32.840
You felt it would just be humiliating!

09:32.840 --> 09:34.300
Isn't that the same for me?

09:34.480 --> 09:35.340
This is absurd.

09:42.080 --> 09:43.140
Look me in the eyes

09:43.160 --> 09:43.870
and tell me—

09:44.440 --> 09:45.550
are you "Mister"?

09:48.440 --> 09:49.030
I'm not.

09:53.320 --> 09:54.320
I'll say it again.

09:55.240 --> 09:57.200
I. Am. Not.

10:09.550 --> 10:10.360
I believe.

10:13.000 --> 10:13.870
I believe you.

10:17.750 --> 10:18.630
I believe you.

10:21.240 --> 10:21.900
You're not.

10:23.580 --> 10:24.300
You're not.

10:28.120 --> 10:28.630
Mom...

10:29.480 --> 10:30.360
Zishan.

10:30.360 --> 10:30.910
Mom...

10:31.850 --> 10:32.870
Mom is here.

10:32.930 --> 10:34.360
Tell me—who is he?

10:35.720 --> 10:36.360
Zishan.

10:37.270 --> 10:37.720
Mom!

10:38.630 --> 10:39.080
Mom...

10:39.320 --> 10:40.620
Mom will protect you.

10:40.650 --> 10:41.030
No.

10:41.030 --> 10:41.550
Tell me.

10:45.840 --> 10:47.080
Don't... Don't...

10:47.080 --> 10:47.750
Don't go.

10:48.430 --> 10:49.830
Don't go looking for him.

10:50.240 --> 10:50.720
Him?

10:51.480 --> 10:52.150
Who is he?

10:53.120 --> 10:53.720
No...

10:54.510 --> 10:55.510
Zishan, who is he?

10:58.120 --> 10:59.270
Who is he, Zishan?

10:59.270 --> 10:59.750
No...

11:02.270 --> 11:03.400
Is the man Luo Liang?

11:04.080 --> 11:04.630
Zishan?

11:04.840 --> 11:05.390
Liang...

11:05.720 --> 11:06.270
Zishan?

11:06.630 --> 11:07.200
Liang...

11:07.750 --> 11:08.720
Is it Luo Liang?

11:09.030 --> 11:09.740
Liang!

11:12.720 --> 11:13.180
Fire...

11:13.800 --> 11:14.950
Fire... Fire!

11:16.200 --> 11:16.960
Together!

11:16.960 --> 11:18.460
Go to hell!

11:18.910 --> 11:19.960
Let go of him!

11:20.550 --> 11:22.440
I'm the one who wants to be with him!

11:22.440 --> 11:23.280
Go away!

11:23.300 --> 11:24.670
His feelings for you are not love!

11:24.670 --> 11:26.150
You can't be with him!

11:26.200 --> 11:28.130
-Let go of me!
-Not unless I'm dead!

11:28.200 --> 11:29.470
Let go of Luo Liang!

11:32.430 --> 11:34.150
-Mom, Mom, no!
-Zishan!

11:34.910 --> 11:35.480
Mom!

11:35.480 --> 11:36.790
-No!
-Zishan, calm down!

11:36.790 --> 11:37.480
Mom!

11:37.960 --> 11:38.790
Mom!

11:38.840 --> 11:39.370
Mom!

11:40.440 --> 11:41.570
-How could she be like this?
-Zishan!

11:41.570 --> 11:42.770
Calm down, Zishan!

11:44.870 --> 11:46.000
What's wrong?

11:46.150 --> 11:47.510
Zishan, calm down!

11:47.550 --> 11:49.310
I'm sorry, Mom! Mom!

11:49.360 --> 11:49.720
Mom,

11:49.720 --> 11:50.460
get up!

11:51.260 --> 11:52.040
I'm sorry!

11:52.310 --> 11:52.790
Mom,

11:52.910 --> 11:53.510
I'm sorry!

11:53.550 --> 11:54.620
Mom!

11:54.910 --> 11:55.360
Mom!

11:55.910 --> 11:56.550
Mom!

11:58.050 --> 11:58.920
Help!

11:59.990 --> 12:00.800
Zishan...

12:04.950 --> 12:05.550
No.

12:10.500 --> 12:11.830
We can't continue.

12:12.360 --> 12:14.290
This memory is too painful for her.

12:14.920 --> 12:17.320
She would rather remain
in her delusion forever

12:17.320 --> 12:19.050
than face it again.

12:19.860 --> 12:21.460
For her, moments of lucidity

12:21.480 --> 12:23.670
are actually a form of suffering.

12:27.550 --> 12:29.370
Doctor? Doctor!

12:29.480 --> 12:31.240
H-How is my daughter?

12:31.360 --> 12:32.860
She's undergoing hypnotherapy.

12:32.860 --> 12:33.840
Try not to worry too much.

12:33.840 --> 12:36.440
Then, when can I take her home?

12:36.440 --> 12:38.360
She can't eat or sleep properly here.

12:38.360 --> 12:40.760
Here's the thing: the police are
still conducting an investigation.

12:40.760 --> 12:42.790
Besides, you and she aren't related,

12:42.790 --> 12:44.270
so we can't let you take her back.

12:44.270 --> 12:46.240
She's in a very unstable state right now

12:46.240 --> 12:48.030
and needs intervention and treatment

12:48.030 --> 12:50.030
from professional psychiatrists.

12:53.320 --> 12:54.180
Dr. Lin!

12:55.150 --> 12:55.790
Coming.

14:09.270 --> 14:09.790
Hello.

14:11.750 --> 14:12.750
How's the person I asked you

14:12.750 --> 14:13.670
to check on?

14:14.360 --> 14:16.090
Wasn't she admitted to the ICU?

14:17.440 --> 14:19.000
Even in the ICU, some patients get better,

14:19.000 --> 14:20.010
and some don't.

14:21.030 --> 14:23.010
There seem to be police at the hospital.

14:23.010 --> 14:25.340
I don't want to bring trouble upon myself.

14:30.320 --> 14:31.050
That's true.

14:31.960 --> 14:32.670
Thank you.

14:35.320 --> 14:35.790
Come on.

14:39.270 --> 14:40.200
It's too stuffy

14:40.200 --> 14:41.240
in the ward.

14:41.440 --> 14:44.100
I want to take her downstairs
for some fresh air.

14:44.440 --> 14:45.650
Is that okay?

14:47.630 --> 14:49.270
We'll be right back up.

14:49.960 --> 14:50.960
Be quick about it.

14:51.360 --> 14:52.080
Okay, okay.

14:52.080 --> 14:53.000
Thank you.

14:53.480 --> 14:54.010
Let's go.

15:05.270 --> 15:05.870
Hurry up.

15:06.440 --> 15:12.790
[Accessible Restroom; Women]

15:08.110 --> 15:08.640
Let's go.

15:30.030 --> 15:30.790
Ma'am.

15:31.840 --> 15:32.570
You're here.

15:33.080 --> 15:33.740
Here you go.

15:34.360 --> 15:34.690
Okay.

15:34.790 --> 15:35.570
Thank you.

15:35.840 --> 15:36.900
Being discharged?

15:37.200 --> 15:38.130
Yes, recovered.

15:43.120 --> 15:44.030
How much is this?

15:44.030 --> 15:44.560
One yuan.

15:45.200 --> 15:45.550
Here.

15:46.150 --> 15:46.550
Okay.

15:47.550 --> 15:49.410
Your accent doesn't sound local.

15:49.480 --> 15:50.810
Where is your hometown?

15:51.630 --> 15:52.440
Diannan.

15:53.960 --> 15:54.820
Thank you.

15:55.030 --> 15:55.690
No problem.

16:01.890 --> 16:05.100
[Dialing]

16:15.560 --> 16:16.740
[Son]

16:22.730 --> 16:24.340
Did he ever tell you

16:24.440 --> 16:27.240
that taking too much of this medicine
can kill you?

16:27.390 --> 16:29.510
Just keep this firmly in your mind!

16:29.720 --> 16:30.630
Not a single day can be missed,

16:30.630 --> 16:31.960
and not a single pill can be skipped!

16:31.960 --> 16:33.840
Feed the medicine to her
exactly as I said.

16:33.840 --> 16:34.600
Not a single day missed,

16:34.600 --> 16:36.660
and not a single pill skipped, got it?

16:49.300 --> 16:50.180
Sorry.

16:50.210 --> 16:53.080
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

16:53.080 --> 16:54.410
Please try again later.

16:54.560 --> 16:55.110
[Ringing]

16:55.110 --> 16:55.730
[Dialing]

16:58.630 --> 16:59.910
Hello. Where to?

17:01.170 --> 17:02.720
The long-distance bus station.

17:02.720 --> 17:03.320
Okay.

17:10.920 --> 17:19.099
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

17:42.070 --> 17:44.470
Your cooking is getting better and better.

17:45.060 --> 17:46.350
Eat more if you like it.

17:49.650 --> 17:54.110
[Welcome to Nanhuguan Service Area]

17:54.150 --> 17:57.180
[Restaurant] [Supermarket]
[Mother & Baby Room] [Toilet]

17:57.160 --> 17:59.400
Let me wipe your hands for you.

17:59.720 --> 18:00.380
That one...

18:01.680 --> 18:02.460
Don't scratch.

18:02.460 --> 18:03.790
Don't scratch. Be good!

18:03.790 --> 18:04.190
Let me.

18:07.030 --> 18:08.360
Alright. Let's go.

18:09.200 --> 18:10.500
Come on. Let's go.

18:10.530 --> 18:11.480
Watch your step.

18:11.480 --> 18:11.880
Right.

18:12.030 --> 18:12.960
Watch your step.

18:13.240 --> 18:13.780
Good.

18:14.000 --> 18:14.830
Good.

18:14.850 --> 18:15.450
Very good.

18:15.480 --> 18:17.280
Let's go. Our bus is over there.

18:18.070 --> 18:19.250
Go home with Mom.

18:19.550 --> 18:21.210
Go back to our Diannan.

18:19.610 --> 18:23.190
[Restaurant] [Supermarket]
[Mother & Baby Room] [Toilet]

18:21.310 --> 18:23.750
Sweet and delicious Sugar-Oil Fritters!

18:24.160 --> 18:26.560
Soft and sticky, Nanhu's local specialty!

18:27.030 --> 18:29.240
Don't miss it when you pass by!
Take a look!

18:29.240 --> 18:30.190
Hungry, huh?

18:30.640 --> 18:32.210
I have food in the bag.

18:34.550 --> 18:35.960
You really want to eat that?

18:35.960 --> 18:37.920
[Tanhua Local Snacks; Sweet, Soft,
Crispy Outside, and Tender Inside]

18:36.200 --> 18:37.480
Thank you.

18:37.480 --> 18:39.640
-Come again if you like it!
-Is it this one?

18:39.640 --> 18:40.970
Is this the one you want?

18:41.350 --> 18:42.170
Sure thing!

18:42.440 --> 18:43.570
I'll pack it for you.

18:44.000 --> 18:44.820
Take care.

18:44.960 --> 18:45.550
Ma'am.

18:46.110 --> 18:47.300
What are these?

18:47.320 --> 18:48.240
These?

18:48.240 --> 18:49.160
These are Sugar-Oil Fritters,

18:49.160 --> 18:50.480
a specialty of our Nanhu.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.450
Taste great.

18:52.070 --> 18:53.830
-One order, please.
-Want some?

18:53.830 --> 18:54.860
To Tanhua!

18:55.030 --> 18:56.830
Any passengers going to Tanhua?

18:56.830 --> 18:57.510
We're leaving now!

18:57.510 --> 18:59.490
Any passengers going to Tanhua?

18:59.320 --> 19:00.910
[Xiangtang] [Tanhua]

18:59.830 --> 19:00.690
We're leaving!

19:01.920 --> 19:02.920
To Tanhua!

19:03.440 --> 19:06.810
To Tanhua! Any passengers going to Tanhua?

19:06.880 --> 19:08.470
My daughter's favorite.

19:08.590 --> 19:09.350
Okay.

19:09.350 --> 19:11.000
Auntie, I'll have one order too.

19:11.000 --> 19:11.740
Coming right up!

19:11.740 --> 19:12.410
How much?

19:12.440 --> 19:13.240
Fifteen yuan.

19:14.030 --> 19:14.350
Okay.

19:14.350 --> 19:15.350
Here's the money.

19:16.310 --> 19:17.210
Thank you.

19:17.960 --> 19:19.220
Are you going to Tanhua?

19:17.990 --> 19:26.880
[Xiangtang] [Tanhua]

19:19.640 --> 19:20.620
This is the bus.

19:22.440 --> 19:23.520
Are there still passengers

19:23.520 --> 19:24.350
going to Tanhua?

19:24.350 --> 19:25.280
Any passengers?

19:25.640 --> 19:26.700
We're leaving now!

19:27.200 --> 19:27.720
Okay.

19:27.720 --> 19:28.500
Zishan.

19:30.720 --> 19:31.720
Zishan!

19:35.000 --> 19:36.400
Zishan!

19:41.200 --> 19:42.220
Fire!

19:43.160 --> 19:43.830
No!

19:44.440 --> 19:45.030
Mom!

19:45.030 --> 19:46.030
No!

19:50.270 --> 19:51.470
It's so tragic.

19:52.820 --> 19:56.280
It turns out Qiao Zishan accidentally
killed her mom herself.

19:56.290 --> 19:58.350
No wonder she had a mental breakdown.

19:59.160 --> 20:01.160
Does that match the autopsy report?

20:01.830 --> 20:02.560
Yes, it does.

20:03.720 --> 20:04.960
Back then, I contacted
the Harbor Island police

20:04.960 --> 20:07.000
and had them scan a copy
of the autopsy report.

20:07.000 --> 20:07.930
The record shows

20:07.940 --> 20:11.270
Qiao Lihua's body did have injuries
consistent with a fall.

20:13.380 --> 20:14.840
This drawing is so pretty.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.820
This girl looks a lot like you.

20:16.940 --> 20:18.910
Who is the boy?

20:20.480 --> 20:21.720
I can't tell you.

20:22.920 --> 20:25.470
He said I can't tell anyone yet.

20:26.550 --> 20:27.770
I have to wait

20:28.200 --> 20:29.680
until Mom agrees.

20:32.550 --> 20:33.200
So...

20:34.070 --> 20:36.480
just because Qiao Lihua
didn't approve of them being together,

20:36.480 --> 20:37.480
Qiao Zishan...

20:38.270 --> 20:39.730
accidentally killed her?

20:41.880 --> 20:44.550
I keep feeling it's not that simple.

20:56.310 --> 20:58.310
Have some hot milk to help you sleep.

20:59.440 --> 21:00.040
Thank you.

21:01.240 --> 21:02.240
It's my fault.

21:03.110 --> 21:04.070
Because of me,

21:04.440 --> 21:05.700
you're worried again.

21:10.400 --> 21:11.440
Don't say that.

21:12.310 --> 21:13.340
We're family.

21:22.110 --> 21:23.170
Hello, who is this?

21:24.160 --> 21:25.240
Su!

21:34.900 --> 21:36.200
Something urgent came up at the hospital.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.260
I need to head over.

21:50.640 --> 21:52.200
Hello, Ms. Yan. What's wrong?

21:52.200 --> 21:53.350
He got a phone call

21:53.840 --> 21:55.510
and then rushed out.

21:55.790 --> 21:58.940
When he left,
he even took his phone charger.

22:00.000 --> 22:00.900
He usually wouldn't

22:00.900 --> 22:04.300
take things like that
when he works overtime at the hospital.

22:05.030 --> 22:07.590
And... the caller was a woman,

22:08.000 --> 22:09.640
and she called him "Su."

22:10.400 --> 22:12.850
I wonder if it might be his mother.

22:13.110 --> 22:14.040
Ms. Yan, Ms. Yan,

22:14.110 --> 22:15.890
you should leave there quickly.

22:15.890 --> 22:17.240
You're acting like an undercover now.

22:17.240 --> 22:18.240
This isn't right.

22:19.110 --> 22:19.960
Gathering evidence

22:19.960 --> 22:20.960
and bringing him to justice

22:20.960 --> 22:22.400
is literally our job.

22:24.580 --> 22:26.960
He has surveillance cameras
installed in the house.

22:26.960 --> 22:27.890
He must have seen

22:28.480 --> 22:29.720
you guys coming to me.

22:33.170 --> 22:38.440
[Stop]

22:54.590 --> 22:55.850
Car rental documents.

23:01.310 --> 23:02.530
If the police come to you,

23:02.530 --> 23:04.390
just say you were feeling very low

23:04.390 --> 23:06.160
and rented a car to kill yourself.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.830
I talked you out of it after we met.

23:07.830 --> 23:09.780
But my car suddenly broke down
when I was about to leave.

23:09.780 --> 23:10.880
I urgently needed a vehicle,

23:10.880 --> 23:11.740
so I took yours.

23:12.150 --> 23:14.200
Other than that, you don't know anything.

23:14.200 --> 23:15.060
What happened?

23:16.160 --> 23:17.200
Remember what I said.

23:17.200 --> 23:18.000
Don't slip up.

23:33.590 --> 23:34.460
You just said

23:36.070 --> 23:36.930
that Luo Liang

23:38.160 --> 23:40.360
has been taking care of that crazy girl.

23:41.000 --> 23:41.440
Yes.

23:43.240 --> 23:44.070
That girl admitted

23:44.070 --> 23:45.790
that she accidentally killed her mom

23:45.790 --> 23:47.000
in the fire back then.

23:47.970 --> 23:50.680
Mister closed
the Amusement Park shortly after.

23:50.680 --> 23:51.880
Maybe the tragedy was so horrific

23:51.880 --> 23:53.210
that it made him flinch.

23:56.750 --> 23:59.180
If Luo Liang really is "Mister"—

23:59.790 --> 24:03.110
someone who didn't care about
all those girls taking their own lives—

24:03.110 --> 24:05.570
would he really be rattled
by one more death?

24:05.790 --> 24:08.680
If that girl was truly brainwashed
by him into

24:08.760 --> 24:11.090
killing her own mother with her own hands,

24:11.590 --> 24:13.240
I think he'd be proud of it,

24:13.410 --> 24:14.150
wouldn't he?

24:15.350 --> 24:16.200
So,

24:16.920 --> 24:20.180
there was another reason
the Amusement Park was shut down?

24:22.200 --> 24:23.340
I'm going back.

24:24.090 --> 24:26.620
Although he said
he wouldn't come back today,

24:26.750 --> 24:28.480
what if he suddenly comes back?

24:28.830 --> 24:29.650
Okay, okay.

24:29.720 --> 24:30.960
Ms. Yan, be careful.

24:30.960 --> 24:31.790
Be very careful.

24:31.790 --> 24:33.720
Call me if anything happens, okay?

24:57.240 --> 24:58.400
I'm at the door.

24:58.720 --> 25:00.780
I cut the fuse to the camera.

25:00.880 --> 25:02.550
The camera shouldn't be working now.

25:02.550 --> 25:03.950
Come open the door for me.

26:12.590 --> 26:14.070
I've checked several times.

26:14.070 --> 26:15.590
Still just those eight cameras,

26:15.590 --> 26:17.050
all in the same positions.

26:45.590 --> 26:46.590
He's so sick.

26:48.680 --> 26:50.000
No normal person

26:50.000 --> 26:52.730
would install so many cameras
in their own house.

26:54.240 --> 26:55.970
Why are you still staying here?

27:01.750 --> 27:02.880
I don't know either.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.350
What do you mean you don't know?

27:04.350 --> 27:05.240
Just move out immediately

27:05.240 --> 27:06.510
and divorce him.

27:08.590 --> 27:11.480
Right now, I'm the person closest to him.

27:14.310 --> 27:15.640
If he really is that man,

27:17.110 --> 27:18.630
and if he slips up,

27:19.510 --> 27:21.510
I'm the only one who might notice it.

27:24.680 --> 27:25.070
Wait,

27:25.830 --> 27:27.000
are you the police?

27:28.110 --> 27:30.310
Why are you locking horns with a psycho?

27:30.790 --> 27:32.320
What if one day he snaps?

27:32.720 --> 27:34.850
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

27:36.070 --> 27:36.720
He won't.

27:38.510 --> 27:41.270
He doesn't get satisfaction
from killing people.

27:41.270 --> 27:42.920
K-Killing people?

27:44.070 --> 27:46.030
I'm telling you, I don't agree with this.

27:46.030 --> 27:47.070
I can't let Jiale

27:47.070 --> 27:48.400
grow up without his mom.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.590
How is Jiale?

27:54.270 --> 27:55.200
He's doing fine.

27:56.680 --> 27:58.280
When I get back, I'll tell him

27:58.310 --> 27:59.510
not to believe a single word

27:59.510 --> 28:00.750
that lunatic said.

28:01.480 --> 28:03.350
No, please don't.

28:04.720 --> 28:05.740
He's still young,

28:06.510 --> 28:07.550
just a child.

28:08.830 --> 28:10.290
If Luo Liang contacts him,

28:11.480 --> 28:15.280
and Jiale accidentally lets
something slip, that would be trouble.

28:16.510 --> 28:17.000
Okay.

28:17.960 --> 28:19.020
I'll listen to you.

28:21.270 --> 28:22.000
Don't worry.

28:22.000 --> 28:24.530
I won't let our son
get caught up in any of this.

28:29.240 --> 28:30.640
You should head back now.

28:32.070 --> 28:34.510
Even though he said
he wouldn't be back tonight,

28:34.510 --> 28:35.370
what if he does?

28:38.240 --> 28:39.790
You're really stubborn.

28:42.880 --> 28:44.210
No matter what happens,

28:44.310 --> 28:45.640
tell me immediately.

28:46.790 --> 28:49.450
This time, I'm sticking with you
no matter what.

29:37.400 --> 29:37.800
Hello?

29:38.070 --> 29:40.270
We just received a report
from Wuzhou People's Hospital,

29:40.270 --> 29:41.510
saying Qiao Zishan is missing.

29:41.510 --> 29:43.030
Hua Sanmei secretly took her away.

29:43.030 --> 29:44.160
We checked the surveillance footage

29:44.160 --> 29:45.640
and the taxi driver's statement,

29:45.640 --> 29:48.020
which show they got on
a long-distance bus to Diannan.

29:48.020 --> 29:49.790
Have you arranged to intercept them?

29:49.790 --> 29:50.400
We notified the checkpoints

29:50.400 --> 29:52.660
and had the bus stopped at a toll station.

29:52.680 --> 29:53.920
But they weren't on the bus—

29:53.920 --> 29:55.590
only Hua Sanmei's travel bag was.

29:55.590 --> 29:57.370
Her phone was inside it.

29:57.640 --> 29:58.400
Okay, got it.

30:03.720 --> 30:04.870
Let's go to my station.

30:04.870 --> 30:05.930
It's very close by.

30:08.310 --> 30:09.710
Luo Liang's birthday...

30:15.130 --> 30:16.250
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

30:20.070 --> 30:21.750
Xiao Su's birthday.

30:21.960 --> 30:23.680
1981-

30:24.000 --> 30:26.200
01-18.

30:27.330 --> 30:28.610
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

30:33.590 --> 30:34.070
Master.

30:35.480 --> 30:36.440
Look at you guys,

30:36.440 --> 30:39.570
turning the station
into a special investigation unit.

30:40.980 --> 30:41.260
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

30:41.500 --> 30:42.150
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

30:44.440 --> 30:46.500
The day the Amusement Park launched.

30:46.680 --> 30:48.920
Officer Li said it was...

30:50.540 --> 30:51.890
[Password hint: Luo Liang]

30:50.870 --> 30:53.450
0102...

30:58.400 --> 30:59.060
Chief Hu,

30:59.090 --> 31:00.310
no records were found
of Luo Liang purchasing plane

31:00.310 --> 31:01.310
or train tickets.

31:01.440 --> 31:01.970
Chief Hu,

31:02.310 --> 31:03.830
we haven't been able to
locate Luo Liang's phone.

31:03.830 --> 31:05.030
He may have switched it off.

31:05.030 --> 31:06.960
And none of the surveillance cameras
between Lihai and Nanhuguan

31:06.960 --> 31:08.690
have captured Luo Liang's car.

31:09.070 --> 31:11.310
It must've been Luo Liang
who instructed his mother

31:11.310 --> 31:12.160
to take Qiao Zishan away

31:12.160 --> 31:14.590
and then get off halfway
to avoid being tracked.

31:14.590 --> 31:15.480
Stop overthinking it, Master.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.740
Let's just arrest him!

31:17.000 --> 31:17.880
Arrest whom?

31:18.240 --> 31:19.170
On what grounds?

31:19.440 --> 31:20.550
Even if we can confirm

31:20.550 --> 31:22.830
he was Qiao Zishan's boyfriend
back in the day

31:22.830 --> 31:24.950
or even confirm he is "Mister,"

31:25.030 --> 31:27.160
there's still nothing we can do to him.

31:27.160 --> 31:28.640
Everything he posted before could,
at most,

31:28.640 --> 31:30.960
be considered a violation
of ethics and decency,

31:30.960 --> 31:32.620
and he deleted it all himself.

31:33.380 --> 31:34.400
No matter what,

31:34.400 --> 31:37.960
Qiao Zishan's disappearance
must have something to do with him.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.760
Let's do this—

31:38.920 --> 31:40.070
check the ride-hailing platforms.

31:40.070 --> 31:40.400
Okay.

31:41.790 --> 31:44.050
I'll look into the car rental companies.

31:54.880 --> 31:56.880
The only bit of light in my childhood

31:57.000 --> 31:58.110
was my sister.

31:59.160 --> 32:00.360
We had a special bond.

32:01.880 --> 32:03.510
We shared the same birthday.

32:05.740 --> 32:07.480
She was exactly 12 years older than me.

32:07.480 --> 32:09.200
1981...

32:10.310 --> 32:11.440
12 years older.

32:12.880 --> 32:14.880
1981... 12 years older...

32:16.480 --> 32:17.590
1969...

32:17.860 --> 32:20.560
[Password hint: Luo Liang]

32:30.630 --> 32:33.810
[Video preview]

32:35.000 --> 32:36.160
Hello, senior.

32:36.680 --> 32:37.610
This is Haoying.

32:38.270 --> 32:40.030
I have an autopsy report
from the Harbor Island police

32:40.030 --> 32:41.720
from several years ago.

32:42.440 --> 32:44.970
I'd like you to help me
take a closer look at it.

32:48.590 --> 32:50.630
[Video preview]

32:50.700 --> 32:52.380
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

32:54.920 --> 32:57.140
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

32:59.090 --> 33:01.300
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

33:02.790 --> 33:04.430
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

33:06.620 --> 33:08.370
[Saturday, July 20, 2019]

33:12.830 --> 33:19.160
1537468905...

33:16.870 --> 33:19.390
[Video preview]

33:19.450 --> 33:21.110
[Police]

33:19.720 --> 33:20.400
There's no ride record

33:20.400 --> 33:23.510
under Luo Liang's phone number
on the ride-hailing platforms.

33:23.510 --> 33:24.680
Ms. Yan, hold on a sec. Hold on.

33:24.680 --> 33:25.480
Master, Master.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.830
Hold on. Hold on.

33:27.070 --> 33:28.000
Master! Master!

33:28.920 --> 33:29.920
Ms. Yan, go ahead.

33:30.070 --> 33:31.920
Through the cameras at home,

33:32.190 --> 33:33.590
[Video preview]

33:32.270 --> 33:34.400
I saw the number that called Luo Liang.

33:35.200 --> 33:36.300
I called it,

33:36.330 --> 33:38.920
and it was a security guard
at a service area in Nanhuguan.

33:38.920 --> 33:41.390
He said an old lady missed her bus

33:41.590 --> 33:43.070
and borrowed his phone to make the call.

33:43.070 --> 33:46.000
She's now staying at
the service area's guesthouse.

33:46.830 --> 33:47.590
You're amazing, Ms. Yan.

33:47.590 --> 33:48.920
You've been a huge help.

33:48.960 --> 33:50.760
Luo Liang must be heading there.

33:51.680 --> 33:53.210
He left the house in a hurry.

33:53.640 --> 33:56.900
I don't think he had arranged it
with his mother in advance.

33:57.640 --> 34:00.070
Ms. Yan, you've done a great job.

34:00.070 --> 34:01.410
Leave the rest to us.

34:01.790 --> 34:04.270
We're currently tracking
his possible travel methods.

34:04.270 --> 34:06.160
So please try to recall

34:06.160 --> 34:07.000
if he has

34:07.000 --> 34:09.060
any close friends who might help him?

34:09.960 --> 34:11.840
Close friends?

34:12.630 --> 34:15.400
For instance, someone
who could lend him a car

34:15.400 --> 34:17.150
or help him rent one.

34:18.110 --> 34:18.770
Officer Li,

34:19.630 --> 34:21.960
could you let me see the car rental list?

34:22.630 --> 34:23.960
I-I'll send it to you right now.

34:23.960 --> 34:25.420
Please wait a sec, Ms. Yan.

34:39.790 --> 34:42.870
[Xu Feng]

34:43.280 --> 34:44.280
Xu Feng?

34:48.389 --> 34:49.469
After we met,

34:49.620 --> 34:51.280
Dr. Luo's car happened to break down.

34:51.280 --> 34:53.510
He was worried
I was too emotional to drive safely,

34:53.510 --> 34:54.989
so he took my car

34:55.150 --> 34:56.670
and told me to take a cab home.

34:56.670 --> 34:57.320
He said he'd

34:57.320 --> 34:59.650
have a repair shop
tow his car the next day.

35:00.190 --> 35:01.230
That's all I know.

35:01.760 --> 35:03.090
So, you lent him the car.

35:03.440 --> 35:05.370
What's your license plate number?

35:08.110 --> 35:09.150
I rented that car.

35:11.360 --> 35:13.160
Thank you for your cooperation!

35:22.030 --> 35:23.150
[Behavioral Neuroscience Research
2019. 07]

35:28.310 --> 35:31.450
[Sort: Ascending/Descending]

35:31.470 --> 35:34.170
[Mind and Society Review-6]

35:34.200 --> 35:35.560
[Chinese Journal of Clinical Psychology,
2018, Issue 6]

35:51.170 --> 35:52.750
[Chinese Journal of Clinical Psychology,
2018, Issue 6]

35:52.770 --> 35:54.400
[Management]

36:04.900 --> 36:06.450
When I was 10,

36:06.690 --> 36:07.940
her boyfriend

36:08.070 --> 36:10.360
got her imprisoned for harboring drugs.

36:11.320 --> 36:13.580
I heard she went south after her release.

36:16.650 --> 36:18.440
She never came back after that.

36:19.360 --> 36:21.360
But his sister had come back.

36:29.760 --> 36:30.790
[Wuzhou Daily]

36:33.130 --> 36:36.120
[The Prairie Speaks to the World]

36:36.350 --> 36:37.500
August 19,

36:37.920 --> 36:39.150
1997...

36:39.500 --> 36:40.820
[A Major Event Shaping
the Future of Spiritual Civilization]

36:42.030 --> 36:45.440
[Body Identification Notice]

36:47.750 --> 36:51.330
[Body Identification Notice]

36:55.030 --> 36:58.270
[Body Identification Notice]

37:20.760 --> 37:22.070
Okay, thank you.

37:23.070 --> 37:25.030
The staff at the service area confirmed

37:25.030 --> 37:27.070
that Qiao Zishan was not with Hua Sanmei.

37:27.070 --> 37:28.440
It was Hua Sanmei alone

37:28.440 --> 37:30.670
who checked into
the service area's guesthouse.

37:30.670 --> 37:33.070
Could it be that Qiao Zishan
ran away halfway,

37:33.070 --> 37:35.330
which is why Hua Sanmei called Luo Liang?

37:35.710 --> 37:36.440
Captain Wang,

37:36.440 --> 37:38.070
we've located Luo Liang's car.

37:38.070 --> 37:39.510
It's indeed on the G60 Expressway,

37:39.510 --> 37:40.760
heading toward Tanhua.

37:40.760 --> 37:42.710
He's 200 kilometers away from Tanhua.

37:42.710 --> 37:45.180
[Tanhua; 200 km]

37:50.590 --> 37:52.320
Send me the location of his car.

37:56.470 --> 37:58.290
[Tanhua; 240 km]

38:44.450 --> 38:49.680
[E.A.S.Y. Clinic]

38:52.540 --> 38:57.010
[E.A.S.Y. Clinic]

38:57.190 --> 38:58.590
Why are you drawing here?

39:04.710 --> 39:06.280
I'm waiting for my mommy.

39:06.630 --> 39:08.490
She's getting her prescription.

39:11.550 --> 39:12.750
What are you drawing?

39:13.150 --> 39:14.210
It's quite pretty.

39:16.550 --> 39:19.630
I'm just... drawing my mommy.

39:20.190 --> 39:23.510
It's about a time when I was little,
on the rooftop of a hospital

39:23.510 --> 39:24.640
back in my hometown.

39:24.880 --> 39:26.740
So you're not from Harbor Island.

39:27.590 --> 39:29.110
I'm from Tanhua.

39:29.670 --> 39:30.730
From the mainland?

39:31.190 --> 39:31.710
Yes.

39:31.710 --> 39:33.440
Me too. I'm from Diannan.

39:34.360 --> 39:35.290
Nice to meet you.

39:35.370 --> 39:38.670
[Adult Psychiatric Clinic]

39:35.760 --> 39:36.890
My name is Luo Liang.

39:37.150 --> 39:38.360
Hello, Dr. Luo.

39:40.320 --> 39:41.920
I'm Qiao Zishan.

39:43.000 --> 39:44.190
Hello. Nice to meet you.

39:44.190 --> 39:45.030
Nice to meet you.

39:45.030 --> 39:47.230
How long have you been on Harbor Island?

39:57.400 --> 39:58.590
You must've been waiting a long time.

39:58.590 --> 39:59.070
No.

39:59.070 --> 39:59.550
No?

40:00.110 --> 40:00.970
This is for you.

40:01.230 --> 40:01.880
What is it?

40:06.110 --> 40:07.400
Sugar-Oil Fritters.

40:07.480 --> 40:09.030
I heard you talking about them every day,

40:09.030 --> 40:11.150
saying you wanted to go back to Tanhua
to have some.

40:11.150 --> 40:12.710
When I went back to Shenchuan,
I searched everywhere

40:12.710 --> 40:14.840
and finally found a shop selling them.

40:48.510 --> 40:49.570
I can't use iodine.

40:51.030 --> 40:53.290
The color of iodine will ruin the tattoo.

40:53.550 --> 40:54.800
It's just a tattoo.

40:56.150 --> 40:57.810
Does it really hurt that much?

40:59.720 --> 41:01.320
No one else reacted like you.

41:01.880 --> 41:02.840
Sorry.

41:05.360 --> 41:06.620
While I was showering,

41:07.110 --> 41:08.480
my mom noticed it.

41:09.840 --> 41:13.100
I was trying to hide it from her
and accidentally got it wet.

41:16.150 --> 41:18.680
You're no longer your mom's
good little girl—

41:18.920 --> 41:21.120
that must have made her very sad, right?

41:21.880 --> 41:22.440
I...

41:23.190 --> 41:23.800
told her

41:25.030 --> 41:26.900
I wanted the tattoo myself.

41:31.150 --> 41:32.550
So you didn't tell her...

41:33.230 --> 41:34.690
this is a token of our love,

41:35.110 --> 41:36.370
proof that you love me?

41:39.230 --> 41:41.850
I just didn't want to make her mad.

41:42.670 --> 41:44.250
I'm with you...

41:44.630 --> 41:46.830
She doesn't want you to be with me at all!

41:47.150 --> 41:49.070
She wants you to go abroad to marry up.

41:49.070 --> 41:51.200
She wants you to marry a rich foreigner

41:51.360 --> 41:52.510
and bring her over.

41:54.480 --> 41:55.410
That's not true.

41:56.280 --> 41:57.710
My mom isn't like that.

41:59.110 --> 42:00.840
Then why did she marry an old man

42:00.920 --> 42:02.380
and come to Harbor Island?

42:03.240 --> 42:05.150
Wasn't she chasing a better life?

42:06.760 --> 42:07.800
Now that she's old

42:08.550 --> 42:10.610
and can't trade on her looks anymore,

42:11.030 --> 42:12.290
she's counting on you.

42:13.130 --> 42:14.860
She wants you to sell yourself.

42:16.760 --> 42:18.000
To her, right now,

42:18.970 --> 42:19.710
I'm just

42:19.710 --> 42:23.640
a poor student preventing you from
marrying rich and rising to the top.

42:29.230 --> 42:30.560
Maybe your mom is right.

42:34.000 --> 42:35.800
You shouldn't have been with me.

42:38.840 --> 42:39.800
No.

42:40.960 --> 42:42.080
It's not like that.

42:43.400 --> 42:45.200
I'm not that kind of person.

42:45.480 --> 42:47.640
I would never do that.

42:47.840 --> 42:49.040
Please believe me.

42:50.840 --> 42:51.800
I swear,

42:52.630 --> 42:54.720
I will never leave you!

43:04.840 --> 43:05.710
I believe you.

43:09.840 --> 43:11.660
I've never doubted you.

43:16.030 --> 43:17.040
The two of us...

43:18.400 --> 43:20.400
are like reflections of each other.

43:21.800 --> 43:24.030
We both came from terrible backgrounds,

43:24.030 --> 43:26.030
with the worst fathers imaginable.

43:28.440 --> 43:29.700
Our meeting

43:30.400 --> 43:31.960
was fated.

43:33.880 --> 43:34.630
We...

43:37.440 --> 43:40.640
are the greatest gift
heaven could have given each other.

43:42.400 --> 43:42.920
Yes.

43:44.960 --> 43:45.590
Yes.

43:48.180 --> 43:49.850
We are one.

43:52.510 --> 43:54.550
No one can separate us.

43:56.340 --> 43:58.530
No one can separate us.

44:03.300 --> 44:07.530
[The Dark Romance]
